persistence:FinderMethod._andromda_hibernate_query: SELECT DISTINCT location FROM Location location WHERE location.neighborhood.id=:idNeighborhood

SELECT product FROM com.com.mogobiz.store.domain.Buyer AS buyer JOIN buyer.sales AS sale JOIN sale.acquisitions AS acqui JOIN acqui.bOPackage AS pack JOIN pack.bOProducts AS product JOIN product.company AS company WHERE buyer.id = :idBuyer AND (acqui.debut is null OR acqui.debut < :dateConsomation) AND (acqui.fin is null OR acqui.unlimited = true OR acqui.fin > :dateConsomation) AND product.externalCode = :codeOffre AND company.id = :idCompany AND product.consumptions.size < acqui.quantity
SELECT sale FROM com.com.mogobiz.store.domain.Buyer AS buyer JOIN buyer.sales AS sale WHERE buyer.id = :idBuyer AND sale.hidden = false
